title: Suleiman the Magnificent ep. 133 (Greek subs) by Stathoun
description:
Suleimanakides geia sas, parte kai to 133 
 epeisodio tis agapimenis mas seiras 
(iperparagogis)
 twn toyrkaladwn poy mas exei kathilosei gia
na goystaretai, se kalyteri analisi
apo to proigoymeno & se morfi mpeg4 gia olous tous players. Paizei & se stick se smart TV 
 gia osous diathetoun. Na eisaste oloi kala & eyxaristo gia ta kala sas logia.Keep seeding.
